               <item n="project_comment_old">&lt;p&gt; [[Schmidt KT 1986]] inserts this fragment into [[THT 1117]]/ Blatt 26 right away - under Blatt 26 (p. 24) he has &lt;i&gt;käl&lt;/i&gt; in line a2, under Fragment H (p. 34) he has &lt;i&gt;kä&lt;/i&gt; only. I have used &lt;i&gt;käl&lt;/i&gt; in all instances here. Please delete if inappropriate! (TI)&lt;/p&gt;</item>
